,"inlineContent":[{"text":"Whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourceProperty"},{"type":"text","text":" is changed the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"targetProperty"},{"type":"text","text":" is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"updated using the same value. For instance:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["  g_object_bind_property (action, \"active\", widget, \"sensitive\", 0);"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Will result in the “sensitive” property of the widget "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object"},{"type":"text","text":" instance to be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"updated with the same value of the “active” property of the action "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"instance."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"flags","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" contains ","type":"text"},{"code":"bidirectional","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the binding will be mutual:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"targetProperty"},{"type":"text","text":" on "},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" changes then the ","type":"text"},{"code":"sourceProperty","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will be updated as well.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The binding will automatically be removed when either the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"type":"text","text":" or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances are f